Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:42.48,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}你所萌生的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:45.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}定是正确无误之志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.11,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}我们怀着同一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:52.34,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}却以为彼此道路相左
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:55.63,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}让我们高举那被遗忘的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:58.37,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}踏荒野前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:02.75,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}盈盈微笑 滚滚泪珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:08.31,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}皆不可遗留于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:12.94,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}夏影倒映 白帜高扬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:20.41,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}那是你我的无名之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:25.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}在遥无尽头的道路彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:29.21,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}那一线光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:31.03,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}牵动万千心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:34.92,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}深信头顶之青空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:40.12,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}启明星高悬东方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.68,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}为我们指引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:49.67,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}{\fad(0,800)}梦想必亲手实现
